com.ostrichemulators.semtool.util

Class GuiUtility

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ostrichemulators.semtool.util.GuiUtility

  • public class GuiUtility
extends Object
    The GuiUtility class contains a variety of miscellaneous functions implemented extensively throughout SEMOSS. Some of these functionalities include getting concept names, printing messages, loading engines, and writing Excel workbooks.
